WEBVTT

00:05.939 --> 00:07.694
- (ALAN) Hello.
- (WOMAN) Hello.

00:07.741 --> 00:10.147
- Josh.
- Oh. Hey, Dad.

00:10.277 --> 00:12.316
Here he is. Big man.

00:12.317 --> 00:14.749
Everybody's very dressed up.

00:15.104 --> 00:17.942
Yep. Yeah, it's a
pleasure to see you too.

00:17.948 --> 00:21.286
Oh, my God, yeah, I have been doing
squats, Dad. Thank you for noticing.

00:21.292 --> 00:22.714
How expensive is this place?

00:22.720 --> 00:25.102
Yeah, okay, I'm buying you
and Mum a nice dinner, okay?

00:25.108 --> 00:27.155
You were worried about Mum,
I was worried about Mum,

00:27.161 --> 00:30.244
and I just I thought it'd be nice
if I bought you guys dinner. Mm-hm?

