Oh, don't be modest. That's...
that is a beautiful shirt.

00:34.757 --> 00:36.178
- Really?
- Mmm.

00:36.184 --> 00:38.292
- I'm not sure about it.
- Mm-hm.

00:38.298 --> 00:40.658
Lock up your daughters,
everyone, 'cause Alan's here.

00:40.664 --> 00:43.867
