with your daughters.

00:43.873 --> 00:45.992
- Thank you.
- Sex things.

00:45.998 --> 00:47.797
- Hey, Ma. Hi.
- Hello!

00:47.803 --> 00:49.627
- Ohh. (CHUCKLES)
- Uh?

00:49.633 --> 00:52.806
- How are you, Rose?
- Oh, yes, good. (CHUCKLES)

00:52.812 --> 00:54.759
- Can I take your coat?
- (ROSE) Oh! Yes.

00:55.417 --> 00:57.472
- I'm Josh's mum.
- Perfect.

